				<td colspan="2"><span>Ok, first of all, notify your group that your mez isnt strong enough to mez the monsters that you are pulling. 
<br />

<br />
Next, if you MUST kite...(ex. dont have another form of CC in group) use a song that does no damage so you wont get summoned.  Ex. Selo's Consonant Chain.  Dont worry about agro, a decent tank should be able to get it off...h*ll...even a warrior with incite should be more agro than snare. =)
<br />

<br />
Keep grouping in BoT...its fast exp and chance of getting decent loot.  Once you get 65, you will have many pulling utilities in your hands (and crowd control as well.)  I recommend getting to 65 ASAP, and than first thing you do is get Fading Memories.  It will save your life more than you can imagine.
<br />

<br />
Dont get down if you have problems, as long as you are learning you are doing good.</span></td>
